data.description: Adorable cottage style farmhouse!  The perfect cozy home in a great North Hall Location.  Just over 1 acre of level yard -- with a barn out back.   Room to garden or build a shop or pool!   The home is a very classic design with original wood floors throughout, shiplap, tongue and groove ceilings, and a remodeled kitchen and bathroom.   Very close to schools, shopping and restaurants.   A great deal at this price point for a small family for a first time home buyer.  Property has apple and pecan trees, grape vines, figs and blueberry bushes.   Lots to enjoy at this fenced property.
